{"content": "I need to multiply 252 \u00d7 115 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 252 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 252\u2081\u2081 = 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 5\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- = 2\u00d7121 + 5\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- = 242 + 55 + 2\n- = 299\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 115 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 115\u2081\u2081 = 1\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 5\u00d711\u2070\n- = 1\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 5\u00d71\n- = 121 + 11 + 5\n- = 137\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 299 \u00d7 137 = 40,963\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 40,963 back to base 11**\n- 40,963 \u00f7 11 = 3,724 R 9\n- 3,724 \u00f7 11 = 338 R 6\n- 338 \u00f7 11 = 30 R 8\n- 30 \u00f7 11 = 2 R 8\n- 2 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 2\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 28869\n\n**Answer: 28869**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 373}